<db:para>Qt's undo framework is an implementation of the Command pattern, which provides advanced undo/redo functionality.</db:para>
<db:para>To show the abilities of the framework, we have implemented a small diagram application in which the diagram items are geometric primitives. You can edit the diagram in the following ways: add, move, change the color of, and delete the items.</db:para>
